summary: FS KKR Capital Corp. (NYSE: FSK), or the Company, today announced its financial and operating results for the quarter ended March 31, 2025, and that its board of directors has declared a second quarter 2025 distribution of $0.70 per share.

headline: Global Atlantic Unveils New Bermuda Office to Accommodate Expansion and Growth
summary: HAMILTON, Bermuda, May 07, 2025--Global Atlantic Financial Group ("Global Atlantic"), a leading insurance company meeting the retirement and life insurance needs of individuals and institutions, today announced a strategic expansion of its Bermuda office into a new, state-of-the-art facility at Washington House, located on Church Street in Hamilton. The move marks a major milestone for the company’s continued growth and investment in the island.
